product.title: Lambert - The Kalei Vegan Leather Card Holder in Black
product.body_html: The KALEI card holder is the perfect size to carry your major cards, money and important bills. The flexibility of the card holder also allows for quick and easy access to your contents. With a clean, minimalist look, KALEI will maximize the space in your backpack or purse with its convenient compartments that maximize storage.
